<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich XVI. von Wittelsbach, Herzog von Bayern-Landshut</head><p>Der Rat kündigt seinen Diener Marquart Waltmann wegen der in Landshut beschlagnahmten Waren von Christian Woltzhofer und anderen Bürgern zu Nürnberg an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="73v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l1">Hercʒog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Baẏern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l2">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als vvir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd nü <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l3">als 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jr cʒu </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade cʒu Kadelcʒſpurg was Peter Kragen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l5">vnd Hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> diener 
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l4">doſelbſthın </ab></add> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l7">von der hab 
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1584618854989_55">vnd ſchulde </ab></add> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / als 
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1584618850793_50"><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab></add> Criſtan wolcʒhofer vnd <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l8"> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu landſhute 
<del rend="strikethrough">aufgeh </del> <expan>beküm<ex>er</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l9">iſt woꝛden / darauf <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l11"><expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l10">ʒu <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab </ab></add> / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> d </del> als ſıe vns geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l12">daʒ vvir darümb ein botſchaft cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gen Lanſhut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l13">tun <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> So vvölle <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hochvvirdikeit die gnedıklich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l14">vnd <expan>auſʒrichte<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd Alſo ſenden vvir <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l15">vvaltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> dauon cʒu reden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l16">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dıener in 
<del rend="strikethrough"> derſel </del> <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l17">ſache cʒu diſem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade werb / daʒ Jr Jm des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l18"><expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="73v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Herczog <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Bayern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und nü
                                <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade
                        czu Kadelczspurg was, Peter Kragen und Hansen
                        <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> diener,
                            <add>doselbsthin</add> czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von der
                        hab <add>und schulde</add>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als <add><expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan></add>
                        Cristan Wolczhofer und <expan>etlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burgern, in
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu Landshute
                                <expan>beküm<ex>er</ex>t</expan> ist worden, darauf
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>hochwirdik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern <expan>gnediklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab</add>, als sie uns gesagt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir darümb ein botschaft czu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> gen Lanshut tun
                            <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan>, so wölle <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        hochwirdikeit die gnediklich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hörn</expan> und
                                <expan>auszrichte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und also senden wir
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> Waltman, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> davon czu reden und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> diener in <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        sache czu disem mal an <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade werb, daz ir im des
                                <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
